column4: hey all, i have a question: i just did a fresh reinstall of Gutsy 64-bit and I want to use Swiftfox instead of regular FF, do i need to install the 32-bit version of FF first in order to get the plugins working? or are their plugins for 64-bit Swiftfox?
I would try asking in a swifox channel
I don't know that there is one,  try checking on their website,  if they have one they will mention it , or try #swiftfox here in this network there might be one,  there is one for everything help
